{"data": [{"id": "4747541", "title": "United Airlines: Why I Sold My Shares (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"United Airlines\" data-id=\"1199330088\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Rusell Hendry</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In early October I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725485-united-airlines-stock-hold-after-recent-take-off\">wrote my first article</a> about United Airlines (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UAL\" title=\"United Airlines Holdings, Inc.\">UAL</a></span>) highlighting why I thought that the recent price appreciation (between August and October) deemed the stock a Hold. Since I was personally invested at the time, I mentioned</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747541-united-airlines-ual-why-i-sold-my-shares-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 01:13:56", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747540", "title": "BHP Group: Solid Free Cash Flow Supports The Yield, Shares Rightly Priced", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Steelworker cleaning pouring end of flask during steel pour in steelworks\" data-id=\"1186090888\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>Iron ore prices were down sharply in 2024; it was the worst year for the industrial commodity </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4391753-iron-ore-caps-worst-annual-drop-since-2015-on-weak-china-demand-high-portside-stocks\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span>since 2015</span></a><span>. A strong US dollar and broad economic weakness in key developed, and emerging countries couldn\u2019t support the price. Not surprisingly, shares</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747540-bhp-group-solid-free-cash-flow-supports-the-yield", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 01:08:05", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747539", "title": "Avery Dennison: Labeling A Better Future", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Avery Dennison manufacturing plant. Avery Dennison is the largest label manufacturer in the world II\" data-id=\"1162604424\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In the final days of 2021, I refused to put a label on shares of <b>Avery Dennison Corporation </b>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVY\" title=\"Avery Dennison Corporation\">AVY</a></span>) after shares had seen very strong share price gains in the period before.</p> <p>Ever since the business has seen</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747539-avery-dennison-labelling-a-better-future", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 00:50:24", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747536", "title": "S&P 500's Long-Term Risk May Produce Contrarian Stock Buys", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Thumbs up and thumbs down\" data-id=\"1485146883\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1129px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Stock picking is tougher than it looks. Your reaction to that statement says a lot about what you've been looking at the past few years. Some stocks have rocketed higher, while many, many stocks have simply spent two years (2023 and 2024) trying to get back</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485146883/image_1485146883.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747536-s-and-p-500s-long-term-risk-may-produce-contrarian-stock-buys", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 00:30:55", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747533", "title": "Peyto: The Winter Campaign Strategy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil pump, oil industry equipment\" data-id=\"1327982065\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://stati