se Derisked Baby Bonds Of Harrow, Inc.", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>I covered Harrow, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HROW\" title=\"Harrow, Inc.\">HROW</a></span>) in </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HROW?s=hrow&amp;source=search\"><span>3 articles</span></a><span> recently, so it is time to sum up my position on Harrow \u2013 and what better way to do that, but by discussing Harrow 11 875 Senior Notes due 2027 (</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747537-those-derisked-baby-bonds-of-harrow-inc", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 23:43:10", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747530", "title": "AOA: An All-In-One Value-Driven ETF", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Investing ecosystem fund and ETF in money market with AI Robot\" data-id=\"2148377205\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">primeimages</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There are many reasons why investors consider buying an exchange-traded fund (ETF) throughout their career. For starters, an ETF provides broader exposure to a wider range of securities, while balancing risk and return.</p> <p>Next to this, some funds provide</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148377205/image_2148377205.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747530-aoa-an-all-in-one-value-driven-etf", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 23:13:56", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747534", "title": "ISM Manufacturing Index Contracts For 9th Straight Month", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Currency and Exchange Stock Chart for Finance and Economy Display\" data-id=\"1358927461\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(1